; Coverage test for format.cc lines 105-107, 114-116
; Test format element parsing:
; - Lines 105-107: expression that consumes the entire remaining format string
;   (str.eof() is true). This happens when the format ends with an expression.
; - Lines 114-116: expression followed by more format text, where trailing
;   whitespace in the expression is backtracked.

2024/01/01 Groceries
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg --format '%(account) %(amount)\n'
Expenses:Food $10.00
Assets:Cash $-10.00
end test

test reg --format '%(account)\n'
Expenses:Food
Assets:Cash
end test
